  "texts": [
    "Models such as ChatGPT are able to adapt conversational style via prompt engineering, so style adaptation is a design challenge rather than a technical challenge.",
    "• Anthropomorphisation.",
    "As LLMs capabilities increase, users are more likely to ascribe personality and agency to them.",
    "This can facilitate building an emotional bond with the App, offering potential benefits such as increased engagement, but also risks such as overreliance on recommendations.",
    "Evidence for this was given by Ma et al. (2024) who reported in an analysis of social media data that some users of an LLMpowered mental health App experienced feelings of stress, loss and grievance after updates to the LLM lead to inconsistent conversational style and the loss of memory of previous conversations."
  ],
